# LLM development — skill index

Mandatory post-change workflow and merge gates live in the always-on **`llm-development-guidelines.mdc`**. Load skills below when triggers match ([`skills/<name>/SKILL.md`](../../skills/README.md)).

| Symptom / task | Skill |
|----------------|-------|
| Changing `upload`, CLI flags, SBOM, artifact results, Tekton paths that run pulp-tool | **changing-pulp-upload** |
| Changing `Dockerfile`, `.tekton/` container builds, Konflux `pulp-tool-container` image | **changing-pulp-container** |
| User confirms PR materials (body, commit message, CHANGELOG) | **drafting-pulp-tool-pr** |
| `make test-diff-coverage` fails or CI diff coverage below 100% | **fixing-diff-cover-failures** |
| Pre-commit or lint loops failing; local vs CI mismatch | **troubleshooting-pulp-tool-ci** |

## Lint quick reference

```bash
make lint && make format
pre-commit run --all-files   # loop until clean
make test                    # full suite; loop until green
git fetch origin && make test-diff-coverage
```

Per-tool detail: `Makefile`, `.pre-commit-config.yaml`, `pyproject.toml`, `.flake8`.

